{"type": "article", "id": 8486, "title": "Nendo 穹顶形纸灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-15T07:18:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234553lQ4qcIKOPpbkuYLx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t日本设计工作室 Nendo 和意大利设计师 Luca Nichetto 联合为威尼斯灯具品牌 Foscarini 推出了这款穹顶形纸灯，已经在灯具展览上展出（米兰家具展单数年举办灯具展，双数年则为厨房家具展）。灯腿材料采用的是日本传统的柏树，纤细的支架支撑着白色的穹顶型灯罩，看上去像是一个慵懒的棉花糖。这次 Luca Nichetto 还展出他的其他作品，如 BonBon 小桌台等。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052345515YXudDcrQIiKWOL7.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234551ex1oT2aiBLIAvhcJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.91452991\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234552sCAm96PZVMaWJiRK.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234552gAGQpURKPBhrH4Wq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234552bH4e6PRBVFT3atzk.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.99786325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}